{"tid":852531,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"兒登仔有冇人識聽Radias？","createTime":"2018-10-08T02:17:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T02:54:08.000Z","uid":206050,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"33093af26a4f31f17ff2680d96969f90795cd250","tid":852531,"uid":206050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:17:51.000Z","msg":"早期啲樂隊組合好正 Beyond之前有太極 達明 仲有個radias <br />\n果時夕爺都岩岩出道<br />\n雖然處女作係幫b哥哥填<br />\n但後來一路做radias御用詞人<br />\n首傳說同吸煙的女人都正到一個點<br />\n傳說入面嘅果堆典故詞唔講<br />\n就講一句：<br />\n自古書裡說梁祝寧願化蝶飛出苦痛我也要化蝶躲入傳說內<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老尾一句呵成正到痴撚曬線<br />\n<br />\n其實當年佢成個專輯都正<br />\n例如某年某日 沒有路人的都市 別人的歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可惜radias第二年就拆夥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059957506a1f89c73140d6f448f56a52d4e91b38","tid":852531,"uid":206050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:22:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kRu2QZrXICY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkRu2QZrXICY&d=iI5Tuu4jwIiV0%2BmkkSMa5S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=b69af756\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kRu2QZrXICY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfafb81b15d137233811e91b1f885148272faef","tid":852531,"uid":115009,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:23:32.000Z","msg":"如何 在你心窗一角<br />\n矇矓呈現我的愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e01b91660802f3670af3a60a0617917efe1b356","tid":852531,"uid":146370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:23:46.000Z","msg":"不斷吐煙 因她不想去習慣"},{"pid":"7f32a8c146d474e6625b3a971f157ed4700f0520","tid":852531,"uid":37719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:24:45.000Z","msg":"淨係識別人的歌"},{"pid":"120eef951472ff7e7b4ef346938be3ff2d25563c","tid":852531,"uid":136519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"99jj<br />\n但勁中意呢隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唱又正，詞又癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實掌聲 屬於那 人盡皆知的歌<br />\n不斷吐煙 因他一早已習慣<br />\n小玉典珠釵 鉛華求長埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a1576b90ab1a46f4619cbbcd2506305d41ac8a","tid":852531,"uid":140218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:31:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Raidas</span>"},{"pid":"acc38c2abb43556770238f185cca739a82ea13e9","tid":852531,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:33:09.000Z","msg":"陳德彰啲唱功勁到"},{"pid":"133edd1b918e9843f32ca56c2ceea4eebb2a0713","tid":852531,"uid":34400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:33:39.000Z","msg":"仲有危險遊戲同杯中冷巷都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw兒你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係又用唔係又用"},{"pid":"34b5032a9e02af67a247c022ecb88af5321f6f0b","tid":852531,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:42:31.000Z","msg":"曾自問樣子真太笨<br />\n曾自問外表都不怎麼吸引<br />\n卻妄想跟你同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba5fafdf3f0321ea51fa72f86c2d0a3469d21e5","tid":852531,"uid":206050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e01b91660802f3670af3a60a0617917efe1b356","tid":852531,"uid":146370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:23:46.000Z","msg":"不斷吐煙 因她不想去習慣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:48:58.000Z","msg":